蹟。當時人們問他是如何算出來，他天真地回答：「想出來的。」<br />\n<br />\n羅文輝成名後曾客串過一齣電影， 短短的電影演出，已經收了2萬5千元片酬，這個銀碼在70年代對客串演出來說是天價。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，根據2007年8月《文匯報》的報道，羅文輝被迫練心算和表演，升中後他更對理科、數學失去興趣，沒有像大眾想像般成為數學家，反而當上肉食工人，按推算現年46歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/65306/%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A5%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%94-%E7%B4%B0%E6%95%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AD%B7%E4%BB%A3%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A5-%E4%B8%83%E6%AD%B2%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%B8%E5%A4%A9%E6%89%8D%E5%81%9A%E8%82%89%E9%A1%9E%E5%88%87%E5%89%B2%E5%93%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F65306%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2598%2594-%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25AB%25A5-%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2589%258D%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%2582%2589%25E9%25A1%259E%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%2593%25A1&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihGyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=81ead310\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/65306/%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A5%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%94-%E7%B4%B0%E6%95%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AD%B7%E4%BB%A3%E7%A5%9E%E7%AB%A5-%E4%B8%83%E6%AD%B2%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%B8%E5%A4%A9%E6%89%8D%E5%81%9A%E8%82%89%E9%A1%9E%E5%88%87%E5%89%B2%E5%93%A1</a>"},{"pid":"f784efb5c8841ace151186d9a432b601bc4ed62d","tid":1152677,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21f97b419e41f61828f9f42aafdbc5ba2691b80e","tid":1152677,"uid":51720,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"心算計微積分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"其實基本運算做到複雜心算<br />\n微積分冇理由唔得<br />\n學少少numerical methods基本上乜都計到"},{"pid":"62f0fad5e19bedb7c17c719a25a4f5a91292367f","tid":1152677,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f784efb5c8841ace1